step 1: npm init -y 
// install required dependencies
step 2: npm install @babel/core 
                    @babel/register  
                    @babel/preset-env 
                    babel-polyfill
                    express morgan chalk 

step 3: create express app ie app.js 
step 4: .babelrc file in root 
    {
    "presets": ["@babel/preset-env"]
    }


step 5:  node entry point - ie start.js 
        require("@babel/register")({});
        module.exports = require("./app");


how to start : nodemon start.js 

----------------
node js with es6 syntaxes